Requirements:
 * SDL (-devel to build)
 * SDL_ttf (-devel to build)
 * scons (to build on Linux, etc..)

See the graf2/ dir for Visual Studio 2008 project files.

Building:
 $ scons

The font verdana.ttf in the execution folder.

Distribution:
